  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: When creating new user **Creating your account on the blockchain...** view and loading indicator appears before name input but should be after it\r\n\r\n<img width=\"374\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-03-02 at 12 22 18 am\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29711298/36872995-d85c7e0e-1daf-11e8-9e11-c4d2f555b48f.png\">\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n**Creating your account on the blockchain...** is shown after name is set\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n**Creating your account on the blockchain...** is shown after password confirmation instead of Name input\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Click Create new account\r\n- Input password\r\n- Input password once to confirm it\r\n- Click Next button\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nStatus version: 0.9.11d.737 (develop build from 01.03.2018)\r\nOperating System: \r\niPhone 8 Plus, iOS 11.1.1\r\nOnePlus 5, Android 8.0.0",
